Package: yoshimi
Architecture: any
Depends:
 yoshimi-data (= ${source:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Recommends:
 jackd,
 yoshimi-doc,
Description: software synthesizer originally based on ZynAddSubFX2
 Yoshimi is a software synthesizer for GNU/Linux, based on
 ZynAddSubFX 2.4.0.
 .
 Yoshimi maintains sound and instrument compatibility
 but now has extended features and accessibility.

Package: yoshimi-data
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends:
 yoshimi,
Description: Presets for Yoshimi
 Yoshimi is a software synthesizer originally based on ZynAddSubFX2
 .
 Yoshimi maintains sound and instrument compatibility
 but now has extended features and accessibility.
 .
 This package provides banks and presets for Yoshimi.

